dct_title_s: Post map of Europe : comprehending England, France, Germany, Italy, &c., with the posts, distances, roads, railways, packet routes, &c.
dct_description_sm: In 40 rectangles of thick paper measuring 21.7 x 11.5 cm. each. Originally folded in covers 22 x 12 cm.
